## FAQs

### How much does the average wedding cost in Spain?

The average cost of a wedding in Spain can vary greatly depending on a multitude of factors such as location, guest list size, and season. Traditionally, the average wedding might range from €20,000 to €30,000. However, intimate weddings or those held during off-peak times may cost less, while more luxurious events can exceed this range.

### How much is a wedding all in?

The total cost of a wedding includes various elements like venue, catering, attire, photography, and more. An all-in wedding in Spain typically costs between €25,000 and €40,000, though this can vary based on personal preferences and specific service choices.

### How much is a wedding planner in Malaga?

Hiring a wedding planner in Malaga usually costs between €1,500 and €5,000, depending on the planner’s experience, the complexity of the wedding, and the services provided. A wedding planner can help manage your special day, ensuring everything runs smoothly while you enjoy the celebration.

